oPTJ("[{\"name\":\"LEDDraw1\",\"type\":\"MatrixDraw\"},{\"name\":\"NoiseLevel2\",\"type\":\"NoiseLevel\"}]\n<xml xmlns=\"https://developers.google.com/blockly/xml\"><block type=\"main_loop\" id=\"e|A637%~?zRb|{K=6;y_\" x=\"113\" y=\"188\"><statement name=\"allCode\"><block type=\"protobject_LEDDraw1_clear_set_4\" id=\"protobject_LEDDraw1_clear_set_4\"><comment pinned=\"false\" h=\"77\" w=\"508\">Borra la pantalla antes de dibujar de nuevo en la siguiente línea.</comment><next><block type=\"protobject_LEDDraw1_drawOnXY_set_2\" id=\"protobject_LEDDraw1_drawOnXY_set_2\"><comment pinned=\"false\" h=\"77\" w=\"530\">Dibuja en la columna X el nivel de ruido. El valor se divide para ajustarlo al rango de la matriz LED y utilizar toda la barra.</comment><value name=\"VAR\"><shadow type=\"math_number\" id=\"ubt+ibR1fTH@wwT.pf[v\"><field name=\"NUM\">1</field></shadow><block type=\"math_arithmetic\" id=\"7g,?eMmt5{~8HpdA~9{)\"><field name=\"OP\">DIVIDE</field><value name=\"A\"><shadow type=\"math_number\" id=\"SNIFshA-eB]jVE8C6w?k\" disabled=\"true\"><field name=\"NUM\">1</field></shadow><block type=\"protobject_NoiseLevel2_get\" id=\"IPaK%/w,Ippv4`6rYxO/\"><field name=\"property\">noise</field></block></value><value name=\"B\"><shadow type=\"math_number\" id=\"_(dh#m5lxk!eoJS:ybg@\"><field name=\"NUM\">15</field></shadow></value></block></value><value name=\"VAR2\"><shadow type=\"math_number\" id=\"=YIfTdcvAta*CjyA:!zC\"><field name=\"NUM\">4</field></shadow></value><value name=\"VAR3\"><shadow type=\"colour_picker\" id=\"kBkj^q`u!ytikskW!~_7\"><field name=\"COLOUR\">#ff4444</field></shadow></value></block></next></block></statement></block></xml>")